                    <foreign xml:lang="gez">ማርያም፡</foreign>
                    </seg>
                    <desc>The word God is rubricated in the first three works; the word Mary is rubricated in the final two works. Occasionally the word God is rubricated in alternating red and black letters (e.g, <locus target="#12r" facs="016">fol. 12r</locus>)</desc>
                    <desc>Columetric layout of text: <locus target="#113v" facs="118">fols. 113v, </locus> (Ps. 150); <locus target="#121v #122r #122v" facs="126 127">121v, 122r, 122v</locus> (tenth biblical canticle)</desc>
